Fy_apt_complex

This map is set in a small Los Angeles apartment complex.  The map is pretty straight forward and contains five main streets with cover positions on the sides of each street. This map would work very well for Gun Game servers too.

-	52 Spawn Points, 26 per team
-	Buy Zones
-	Nav File for bots
-	Overview radar map included
-	3d Skybox
-	Cube maps
-	All files compiled into the bsp using Pakrat

Blair (Bobpoblo) Burkhardt - Level Design
http://www.fpsbanana.com/members/776402
